data.description: Back on the market! One person's lost is another's treasure.  VA appraisal - appraised to $532,000.  Beautiful huge corner lot property equipped with all the bells and whistles! This beautiful Forest Park Homes boasts 5 bedrooms, 5 bathrooms, high end finishes, designer lighting, a huge 2 car garage with parking pad infront of it, porches, decks, and an open floor plan with over 4,000 square feet of finished living space. The first floor features a large living space  with a fire place, double sliding doors with access to a side porch and yard space. The gourmet kitchen features stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, a 5 burner stove, and extends off to a large deck off the kitchen to the huge rear yard. The second floor offers an owner suite with a custom bathroom that has a 7 ft standing shower, a soaking tub, a linen closet as well as a walk in closet; 2 additional large bedrooms, a full hall bathroom, and laundry room. The third floor offers an additional 2 spacious bedrooms and storage space. The finished basements includes a full bathroom, yard access, and lots of space.  This home is located walking distance to Forest Park golf course, close approximate to downtown harbor, major highways, and other nearby attractions including fine restaurants, malls, recently renovated Hanlon Reservoir, Druid Hill Park, Howard Peters Conservatory and Botanical Gardens, Jones Falls Trails, City Farms Garden, and more.
